data.description: Don't miss this opportunity! This is a convenient located  completely renovated East Nashville home! Great location and walking distance to many of East Nashville hot spots. This is a 3 bedroom 2 bath home that is perfect for rental  income, air bnb, or first time buyer. The roof and central unit are less than 3 years old. Home has  two driveway access and open lot in the back for additional build. Home has new floors, new  paint, and new light fixtures, and 2 wood  working out buildings with electric plus extra  shed for storage. Home also offers two  balconies off the top floor for sitting out and  privacy. This home is adorable and move-in  ready. Its a must see in the historic area of East  Nashville! Bring offer! Home has extra driveway going to back lot where someone could build on. Home has a new sink in the kitchen also.
